{"tid":1930610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鳩融侄女隻狗中武肺之後死左！！","createTime":"2020-03-17T16:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T16:21:39.000Z","uid":236171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0030736e8e3bfeafe78d7bc9450442cc263511b3","tid":1930610,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球首隻染疫動物　<br />\n女馬主周巧兒松鼠狗離世</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n之前確診新冠肺炎，現已出院的女馬主周巧兒，其飼養的17歲松鼠狗也曾一度確診。漁農自然護理署今日(17日)接受傳媒查詢時表示，該狗隻已於昨日(16日)死亡。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署表示，署方從有關畜養人得悉，該狗隻已於昨日離世。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畜養人表示不願意為狗隻進行驗屍確定死因。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b3fba7590b8e8d5397fdb3771cf4cd93b15bc568","tid":1930610,"uid":199517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"一家人最緊要齊齊整整.JPG"},{"pid":"e5354bb8d19c3c83b35111ddc8d90910a6940a22","tid":1930610,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"cls 支那武漢人工病毒肺炎連動物都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155aafdd55429322e1bd7d7fb3b94188a4196595","tid":1930610,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"跟錯主人就會有呢個下場"},{"pid":"eb49dcb047775c375bf52c1cf9cddbd9de15c93b","tid":1930610,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"邊個同狗有親密接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0445eb04b015d1b43ec43c9a969d151dc3fd4b5a","tid":1930610,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"CLS唔係話驗到陰性出院咩<br />\n又會突然死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\